        <abstract> 
<p>Comments on the response to <hi rend="italic">Movement in plants</hi>, which seems to have been successful.</p>  
<p>Is going over revises of <hi rend="italic">Earthworms</hi>.</p> 
            <p>Is investigating further his notion that leaves align themselves in the rain so as to shoot off drops of water.</p>
        </abstract>
